WEBVTT

00:09:58.215 --> 00:10:00.912
run an extra mile to save other people,

00:10:00.936 --> 00:10:03.649
no matter who they are,
no matter what religion,

00:10:03.673 --> 00:10:06.565
no matter who, where they come from.

00:10:06.589 --> 00:10:08.350
We all want to be heroes.

00:10:08.374 --> 00:10:11.736
We just need a good idea, motivation

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:13.571
and lots of chutzpah,

00:10:13.595 --> 00:10:15.736
and we could save millions of people

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:17.908
that otherwise would not be saved.

00:10:17.932 --> 00:10:19.593
Thank you very much.

00:10:19.617 --> 00:10:24.587
(Applause)